      "span_id": "p192_s0003",
      "text": "6.6.8.2  Login Extension Data Length",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        270.37,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0004",
      "text": "If the Login Extension Data Length field (word 31) is non-zero, a Login Extension follows the normal",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        82.97,
        539.98,
        94.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0005",
      "text": "payload.  The Login Extension Data Length field indicates the length of the Login Extension field in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        94.97,
        539.85,
        106.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0006",
      "text": "words.  The Payload Bit (see 6.6.2.4.19) shall be set to one if this field is non-zero.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        106.97,
        460.5,
        118.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0007",
      "text": "6.6.8.3  Login Extension format",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        130.97,
        243.75,
        142.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0008",
      "text": "The Login Extension field is a sequence of zero or more Login Extension Pages.  The length in words",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        154.96,
        540.01,
        166.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0009",
      "text": "of the sequence of Login Extension Pages shall be equal to the value of the Login Extension Length",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        166.96,
        539.96,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0010",
      "text": "field.  The format of a Login Extension Page is given in Table 171.  Word 0 of the first Login Exten-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        178.96,
        539.92,
        190.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p192_s0011",
      "text": "sion Page, if present, is word 64 of the FLOGI/PLOGI/ACC payload.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        396.52,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
